Notes: Pardot API v5 is current. Uses Salesforce Marketing Cloud Account Engagement.
Amplitude HTTP API v2 is current. Batch API recommended for high volume.
Braze REST API does not use explicit versioning in URLs. Uses rolling updates.
DV360 API v2 is outdated. v4 is latest; v3 is being deprecated.
SendGrid Web API v3 is current. v2 was deprecated.
Facebook Graph API versions are typically supported for 2 years. v21.0 was released in Oct 2024; v22.0 is latest as of Nov 2024. Older versions below v18.0 are deprecated.
Uses Facebook Marketing API. Same lifecycle as Graph API - versions supported for ~2 years.
Display & Video 360 API v4 is latest. v3 is being phased out.
GA4 Measurement Protocol v2 is the current version. Replaces deprecated Universal Analytics.
Uses Google Ads API. v21 is latest stable; v19 is still supported.
Google Sheets API v4 is current and stable.
HubSpot CRM API v3 is current. v1 was deprecated in 2022.
Intercom uses API version headers (Intercom-Version). Latest is 2.11.
Klaviyo uses date-based versioning (YYYY-MM-DD format). Latest is 2024-10-15.
LinkedIn Marketing API uses v2.
Mixpanel Ingestion API is current. No explicit versioning in most endpoints.
Pinterest API v5 is current.
Salesforce releases 3 versions per year. v53.0 is from 2022. Current is v60.0 (Winter '25). Versions are retired 3 years after release.
SendGrid Web API v3 is current and stable.
Snapchat Conversions API v3 is current.
TikTok Events API v1.3 is current.
Twilio API uses date-based versioning. 2010-04-01 is stable and maintained.
